    "originContent": "<p align=\"center\">A fast, single-binary watermarking tool for images and PDFs. Built in Rust.</p>",
    "translatedContent": "<p align=\"center\">画像とPDFのための高速な単一バイナリ透かしツール。Rustで構築。</p>"
  },
  {
    "row": 8,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 9,
    "rowsha": "VjeEy91Dri45XyH43cn+3yHOPhxn2sANJxxqT+VYGtc=",
    "originContent": "## Why watermark your documents?",
    "translatedContent": "## なぜドキュメントに透かしを入れるのか？"
  },
  {
    "row": 10,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 11,
    "rowsha": "lt6o6fhNB9PRKREuOh9cj+ZXc9PXVtb7UgTI1Z9BWaE=",
    "originContent": "Every year, millions of people fall victim to identity fraud that starts with a",
    "translatedContent": "毎年、何百万人もの人々が単純なドキュメント交換から始まる"
  },
  {
    "row": 12,
    "rowsha": "icHg36oRATOPQnM8+lkkOWdoU3DVIsAIPEYUodbbzCE=",
    "originContent": "simple document exchange. A common scenario: you're looking for a flat to rent.",
    "translatedContent": "身分詐欺の被害に遭っています。よくあるシナリオ：あなたは賃貸物件を探しています。"
  },
  {
    "row": 13,
    "rowsha": "qoxES8Js7cPrqpCDvOA69k1ewDD7mUWWvFtmDNyvvmQ=",
    "originContent": "The landlord — or someone posing as one — asks for a copy of your ID, a pay",
    "translatedContent": "大家さん、またはそれを装う誰かが、あなたのIDのコピー、給与明細、税通知書を要求します。"
  },
  {
    "row": 14,
    "rowsha": "clgovFkjycmeuGsNjdyjzYpxDBrV9dItvl7N24P1P1Q=",
    "originContent": "stub, a tax notice. You send them unmarked. The \"landlord\" disappears, and your",
    "translatedContent": "あなたは透かしなしで送ります。「大家さん」は姿を消し、"
  },
  {
    "row": 15,
    "rowsha": "l77/06iA/wntmfYLEumNfyJZ2QJGy0dn3eV71OF2rog=",
    "originContent": "documents are now used to open bank accounts, take out loans, or forge",
    "translatedContent": "あなたの書類は銀行口座の開設、ローンの借入、または"
  },
  {
    "row": 16,
    "rowsha": "VfsoHJEsFvpUYyKGnlL8+/b6Z064ww9AyFtE2pprc6s=",
    "originContent": "identities in your name.",
    "translatedContent": "あなたの名前を使った身分詐称に利用されます。"
  },
  {
    "row": 17,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 18,
    "rowsha": "a4nlG3fzkWWadWqX3vW//zzFbjdH3n4oNsuRTItT6O0=",
    "originContent": "Watermarking every document you send out is the single most effective defence.",
    "translatedContent": "送るすべてのドキュメントに透かしを入れることが最も効果的な防御策です。"
  },
  {
    "row": 19,
    "rowsha": "QXjV4Vjn2JvsST7ZV+YAxHbRl/YpGVX5SuF0KXnZmok=",
    "originContent": "A visible overlay that reads **\"Sent to XYZ agency — March 2026 — flat rental",
    "translatedContent": "「XYZ機関に送信済み — 2026年3月 — 賃貸申請用のみ」という"
  },
  {
    "row": 20,
    "rowsha": "hiQTbmMruVgliuwOXJgRkN07DT6zC8YUla/15sy/T64=",
    "originContent": "application only\"** makes the document useless for any other purpose. If it",
    "translatedContent": "目に見えるオーバーレイは、他の目的には書類を無効にします。もし"
  },
  {
    "row": 21,
    "rowsha": "D4PlMrb+EgKG6XOUvVz6Hkb92It4dFzFnRsRxiKAKSE=",
    "originContent": "leaks, you know exactly where it came from.",
    "translatedContent": "漏れた場合でも、どこから来たのか正確に分かります。"
  },
  {
    "row": 22,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 23,
    "rowsha": "XkUZc7HWJz1/PAkrf2IutbkLhGNsglrSDRG1FnylCMs=",
    "originContent": "firemark makes this effortless: one command, any image or PDF, 17 visual",
    "translatedContent": "firemarkはこれを簡単にします：ワンコマンドで、任意の画像またはPDFに、"
  },
  {
    "row": 24,
    "rowsha": "TDNNiiAM1dBtcaRMcGY6miIGPIUL/ntJuB3vBmJ/4Yo=",
    "originContent": "styles, cryptographic filigrane patterns that resist editing, and batch",
    "translatedContent": "17種類の視覚スタイル、編集に強い暗号学的フィリグラーネパターン、"
  },
  {
    "row": 25,
    "rowsha": "5BRet9Zhqz8D1tR00lHTiu68ReT8/ak7LOdTMfW9y3s=",
    "originContent": "processing for entire folders.",
    "translatedContent": "そしてフォルダ全体のバッチ処理が可能です。"
  },
